    <Section title='About'>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        Polyglot engineer with 10+ years building production systems specializing in web technologies and their
        associated infrastructure. Experienced in PHP, Node.js, .NET, Python, GoLang and React, with extensive
        experience in AWS, Azure and Kubernetes environments. Advocate and contributor for Open Source, passionate about
        transparency, analytics, and pragmatic AI/Automation in buisness solutions.
      </p>
    </Section>
